OOC: NOTE: G1 Rampage left the CF a while ago =)

::Razorclaw/Divebomb/Rampage/Astroblast::

Razorclaw catches Autofire's message, and nods in agreement. He 
then jumps into flight, over top of Khonkolor's machine gun fire, and 
provides cover fire in the form of eight concussion blasts towards 
Halucigen and Khonkolor.

---------

Divebomb also hears Autofire, and his instincts help him as he 
rises slowly. "Ughnnnhhg," he spits, and transforms, rocket 
boosters propelling him quickly away from the CF, and towards the 
Dark Avian.

----------

Rampage reaches the Dark Avian to find Megatron, Motormaster, 
Astroblast, and Switchblade out front, "Too... many," He utters as 
he arrives, "I want to destroy, destroy, destr..." He falls into stasis 
lock, and Tantrum falls on top of him.

Astroblast is the first to notice them, as they show up on his radar, 
"Megatron, we have two Decepticon incommings, looks like... well, 
I'm not sure, but I'd say that those are two Predacons, Rampage 
and Tantrum." As the bots land, "They look toasted. Hehe." He 
finishes with a small laugh.
